Destra Investment Trust - Destra Focused Equity Fund: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 28, 2017 9:11 AM ET
Capital Markets

Company Overview of Destra Investment Trust - Destra Focused Equity Fund



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Destra Investment Trust - Destra Focused Equity Fund is an open-ended equity mutual fund launched and managed by Destra Capital Advisors LLC. The fund is co-managed by WestEnd Advisors, LLC. It invests in the public equity markets of the United States. The fund invests in stocks of companies operating across diversified sectors. It invests in growth, value, and growth-oriented value stocks of large-cap companies. The fund employs fundamental analysis with a top-down stock selection approach focusing on factors like low debt-to-equity ratios, high return-on-equity, earnings growth opportunity strong competitive position, prospective benefits from secular tailwinds, and a proven management tea...
Destra Investment Trust - Destra Focused Equity Fund is an open-ended equity mutual fund launched and managed by Destra Capital Advisors LLC. The fund is co-managed by WestEnd Advisors, LLC. It invests in the public equity markets of the United States. The fund invests in stocks of companies operating across diversified sectors. It invests in growth, value, and growth-oriented value stocks of large-cap companies. The fund employs fundamental analysis with a top-down stock selection approach focusing on factors like low debt-to-equity ratios, high return-on-equity, earnings growth opportunity strong competitive position, prospective benefits from secular tailwinds, and a proven management team to create its portfolio. It benchmarks the performance of its portfolio against the S&P 500 Index. The fund uses proprietary techniques to create its portfolio. It was formerly known as Destra Investment Trust II - Destra Focused Equity Fund. Destra Investment Trust - Destra Focused Equity Fund was formed on April 12, 2011 and is domiciled in the United States.
Detailed Description


901 Warrenville RoadSuite 15Lisle, IL 60532United StatesFounded in 2011



