Destra Investment Trust - Destra Focused Equity Fund Key Developments

Destra Investment Trust II - Destra Focused Equity Fund, Special/Extraordinary Shareholders Meeting, Oct 15, 2015
Aug 24 15
Destra Investment Trust II - Destra Focused Equity Fund, Special/Extraordinary Shareholders Meeting, Oct 15, 2015., at 10:00 Central Daylight. Location: the offices of Chapman and Cutler LLP. Agenda: To approve a new investment sub-advisory agreement by and among Destra Capital Advisors LLC, WestEnd Advisors LLC and Destra Investment Trust II, on behalf of the company; and to transact such other business as may properly come before the meeting.


