Destra Investments may pay to your financial intermediary a commission rate of  
1.00% of the net asset value of the Class C shares purchased. Service providers 
to qualified plans will not be eligible to receive this commission if they      
receive 12b-1 fees from the time of initial investment of qualified plan assets 
in Class C shares.                                                              

