      5. Issue any senior security except as otherwise permitted (i) under
         the 1940 Act or (ii) pursuant to a rule, order or interpretation issued
by the SEC or its staff.                                      

      6. Borrow money, except as otherwise permitted under the 1940 Act or
      pursuant to a rule, order or interpretation issued by the SEC or its
